  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, IManifestHandler<BinaryManifestActivity,​BinaryManifestService,​BinaryManifestContentProvider,​BinaryManifestBroadcastReceiver>
    public class ProcessManifest
extends BaseProcessManifest<BinaryManifestActivity,​BinaryManifestService,​BinaryManifestContentProvider,​BinaryManifestBroadcastReceiver>
    This class provides easy access to all data of an AppManifest.
    Nodes and attributes of a parsed manifest can be changed. A new byte compressed manifest considering the changes can be generated.
    Author:
    Steven Arzt, Stefan Haas, Mario Schlipf
    See Also:
    App Manifest
